 &ldquo;Woah!&rdquo;
Mecis looked on in awe as she saw her fellow SeeD catapult out of the Lunar Base at incredible speed. She looked up to her companions. &ldquo;That&rsquo;s amazing.&rdquo;
Kai simply nodded at her. He had seen all this before, and every time a new SeeD came to watch the launch process the reaction was always the same.

Hopefully, the site is now Netscape-safe&hellip;
Uploaded more stuff today: I put up an ECE Board Exam Reviewer — it&rsquo;s a software that helps me review for the upcoming ECE boards. It&rsquo;s in the files section. I really should add that to the list of resolutions: WILL STUDY FOR BOARD EXAM!
I also decided to renovate and re-use the geocities site so I put up an Anime ROMs site there. I wanted to put up the Anime ROMs before, but I was worried about what Topcities might do, since Ihaven&rsquo;t heard anything about what they do to copyright violations on member sites.
